david porter (born july 6, 1949 in bowmanville, ontario) was a canadian ice dancer. with partner barbara berezowski, he won two gold medals at the canadian figure skating championships and competed at the 1976 winter olympics. on october 23, 2008, porter was inducted into the scuggog sports wall of fame in port perry, ontario. currently, porter is the president of port fire pyrotechnics and special effects and its consumer fireworks subsidiary, wizard pyrotechnics.